      "individualData": {
        "pmid": "PMID:41820796",
        "title": "Expanding the Prenatal Phenotypic Spectrum of TRPV6 Variants With Ocular Anomalies.",
        "individualId": "fetus-1",
        "comment": "Bilateral cataracts and bilateral corneal opacities were observed; bilateral modifiers were manually added to the exported Phenopacket. Compound heterozygous TRPV6 variants were confirmed in trans: NM_018646.6:c.1465G>A, p.(Gly489Arg), maternally inherited; and NM_018646.6:c.1286A>G, p.(Glu429Gly), paternally inherited. Both variants were classified as likely pathogenic in the publication.",
